data.description: In need of space? This two-story home boasts 4 spacious bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and a convenient 2 car garage. Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a large entrance with high ceilings and a versatile flex room that can be customized to suit your lifestyle, whether it is a home office, a playroom, or a stylish den for relaxation. The kitchen offers granite countertops and all stainless steel appliances. Enjoy gatherings in the large living room featuring a cozy warm fireplace. As you ascend the staircase to the upper level, you'll discover a small loft and bonus room, perfect for movie nights, a game room, a guest room, or your private retreat. The possibilities are endless in this home. Exterior offers a wood-fenced backyard with mature trees and a creek that runs through the back of the property. Don't miss out on this one!
